2: head; 3: fore leg; 4: mid leg; 5: hind leg; 6: wing; 7, 9: hypopygium in left lateral view; 8, 10: hypopygium in right lateral view. 3–6: Scale bars=0.2mm; 2, 7–10: Scale bars=0.05mm.
